On this episode of the Major Issues Podcast we go down, down, down the road of recapping and reviewing the latest project to come out of the MCU, Agatha All Along! Join us as we discuss the themes the show presents, gush over the costume design, and try our best to predict what's next for favorite witch (or witches) and the future of magic of the MCU. Take of your shoes, grab some chalk and a pinch of salt and follow me my friend...to glory at the end!

Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

 

